Some policemen opened fire on a secondary school girl while dispersing protesting members of the Islamic Movement in Nigeria  (IMN ) at Wuse market in Abuja on Wednesday. A witness said that the girl was returning from Government Secondary School Wuse when she was shot, reports online newspaper, TheCable. Two journalists, who were covering the incident, were arrested. One of the arrested reporters is Afolabi Sotunde of Reuters. Details to followâ€¦ 